<div class="sub-content-header">It’s Almost Time to Update Your Directory Listing </div>
<br />

<IMG style="MARGIN-TOP: 0px; MARGIN-LEFT: 5px" hspace=5 align=right src="/images/content/2011_CES_Directory_Cover.JPG" width=119 height=160>Calling all 2012 International CES exhibitors!&nbsp; It’s almost that time of year for you to review and approve your company data coming live in early July on the exhibitor directory on <A href="http://www.cesweb.org">CESweb.org</A>. This important step in verifying your company information ensures that attendees viewing your online directory company listing (and later this fall, your company listing on the official interactive floor plan) are seeing the most up-to-date company info. More details to follow in the coming weeks!&nbsp; <BR><BR>If, when an attendee is viewing your online listing, you want to make a lasting impression, take a minute now to <A href="http://www.mapyourshow.com/info/CES_2012_MarketingOpps.pdf" target=_blank>review the digital marketing packages</A>. They’ve been designed to engage your audience, distinguish your company among your competitive field and elevate you from the 2,800 other exhibitors. <A href="mailto: brett@mapyourshow.com">Contact Brett</A> to learn more.<BR>
